          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">England</ENAMEX>, among <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">members</ENAMEX> who were receiving
          antihypertensive <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">medication</ENAMEX> from <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1992 to 1994</TIMEX>. Automated
