          <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">members</ENAMEX> for <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">at least three months</TIMEX>, were at least 18 years
          of age, and carried a diagnosis of <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">hypertension</ENAMEX>. Only
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individuals</ENAMEX> on single-drug therapy for high blood
