          participate. In addition, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">42</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">subjects</ENAMEX> dropped out midway
          through the study, and <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">44</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individuals</ENAMEX> were later excluded
          because of indications of improper use of their
