          doses at an opening or incomplete closure of the
          medication vial. The remaining <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">286</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> constituted
          the study <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">population</ENAMEX> for this investigation. <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Individuals</ENAMEX>
          who were eligible but did not complete this investigation
