          <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">days</TIMEX>. Our previous study [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">15</TIMEX> ] had indicated that
          responses to this <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">item</ENAMEX> (compared with <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4</NUMEX> other adherence
          items) correlated most closely with adherence as measured
