          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Social</ENAMEX> support was assessed using a <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">9</NUMEX>-item inventory.
          The inventory inquired about how often the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">participant</ENAMEX>
