          occur within <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">15 minutes</TIMEX> of each other to prevent
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">artifactual</ENAMEX> inflation of the number of dosing events.
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Data</ENAMEX> were downloaded from the cap to a personal computer
