          <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Two to three weeks</TIMEX> after completion of electronic
          monitoring, a followup questionnaire was sent to
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> to update information on their socioeconomic
          status, prescribed antihypertensive therapy,
